doc.after: Yellowstone is a Boeing Commercial Airplanes project to replace its entire civil aircraft portfolio with advanced technology aircraft New technologies to be introduced include composite aerostructures more electrical systems reduction of hydraulic systems and more fuel efficient turbofan engines such as the Pratt Whitney PW1000G Geared Turbofan General Electric GEnx the CFM International LEAP56 and the Rolls Royce Trent 1000 The term Yellowstone refers to the technologies while Y1 through Y3 refer to the actual aircraft 1
